<p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9988px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">岁月悠悠忽已晚，不忧不惧尽欢颜。为进一步加强班团一体化及我院班团干部队伍建设，使班团干部工作规范化、制度化，更好地服务同学，经济管理学院班团联合会于11月8日10：00在经济管理学院一楼大厅开展班团委换届选举大会。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714460229013077665.jpg" title="1714460229013077665.jpg" alt="e81bc424e9e39992636f9aafc2064ae7.jpg" width="1" height="1" style="width: 1px; height: 1px;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.2142em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我是来自B220504班的班长余盈盈，现任班团联合会会长。很荣幸学院能够给予我以认可与信任，让我能够在班团这个跳板上不断锻炼自我、提升自我。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.2142em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">在任职期间，我会始终保持奋发有为的状态，满怀敢闯敢拼的斗志以及开拓进取的精神，尽我所能将班团带上一个新高度。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.2142em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">俗话说一点一滴汇成大海，一沙一砾集成沙漠，一步一行可达万里。我想—脚踏实地、慢慢来是我最大的诚意。希望班团在我的带领下，可以充分展现出经管学子积极开朗的精神风貌，将经管的特色推广出去，同时把握好发展契机，不断在实践中创新并发展班团模式，为学院与班级之间搭建好沟通的平台，切切实实落实好学院工作安排，助推学院发展。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714460343358090332.jpg" title="1714460343358090332.jpg" alt="f8af65e97b822b839801af69722d00e2.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.2142em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我是班团联合会副负责人魏智。首先很感谢大家对我信任与支持，也感谢老师们还有学长学姐们的细心教导。希望在接下来的时间里，我们这个大家庭可以一起互相配合，共同进步。有什么问题我们可以一起讨论解决一起成长。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.2142em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">作为班干的我们应该带头积极踊跃参加学院的各项活动，呼吁班上的同学们积极参加。和你们这群优秀可爱的小伙伴们共事是我的荣幸。我们也会在一次次工作中不断学习锻炼自己。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.2142em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我们一起营造良好的班团氛围，提高班团间的凝聚力，为学院更好的发展形成一股活跃、团结的力量。知不足而奋进，望远山而前行！</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714460642932040637.jpg" title="1714460642932040637.jpg" alt="2cc561df0a41fa019402232c82b82374.jpg" width="743" height="434" style="width: 743px; height: 434px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.2142em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9988px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我是组织委员徐雨欣，我认为班团是一个团结、友爱、互助、进步的大家庭。作为组织委员，我会尽自己最大的努力，为大家服务，为班团做出更多贡献。也希望能够与大家一起，共同进步，共同成长。我相信，只要我们一起努力，我们的班团一定会更加团结、更加进步、更加美好！</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9988px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714460603828077779.jpg" title="1714460603828077779.jpg" alt="0ca0e8f7f1d234396227cc4f4dfbe832.jpg" width="741" height="518" style="width: 741px; height: 518px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.2142em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9988px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我是C220515班的团支书张金平。作为班团宣传委员，通过各种渠道宣传班团的学风、团队精神，各类宣传活动和活动成果等等。为班团的发展、同学们的成长和宣传工作提供支持和推动。最后，感谢大家的支持和信任，我相信，只要我们团结一心，共同努力，我们一定能够打造一个<span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9988px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">充满活力、温暖和进步的班团！</span></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714460556396061759.jpg" title="1714460556396061759.jpg" alt="5c3255643a614c94a277d5a6c3bf3764.jpg" width="787" height="537" style="width: 787px; height: 537px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.2142em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">至此，本届班团联合会换届大会圆满结束，希望各位同学可以继续保持优良习惯，全面提升自己，奋勇争先，勤奋刻苦，成为更加优秀的人。相信在班团联合会成员的工作和指导下，我们经济管理学院能够更上一层楼。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"></p>